								<p><h4>Web Browser and Search Engines</h4></p>
								<p>The most common software used on the Internet is a Web browser, usually just called a browser.</p>
								<p>A browser is a software program that allows the computer to access to the Web and allows the user to look through or "browse"ù information on Web sites and Web pages.</p>
								<p><strong>Popular browsers are Internet Explorer, Mozilla Firefox, Google Chrome, and Safari, among others.</strong></p>


